		=' where all interested parties can see how different oil prices affect the money available for the 2015 budget. Others, such as '
		a(href='http://www.globalwitness.org/ugandaoilcontracts/')  Global Witness
		=' , have used this to model hypothetical oil projects, using contract information, while IMF economists routinely use (and stress '
		a(href='http://www.imfbookstore.org/ProdDetails.asp?ID=NRRAHEA')  the importance of
